SourceCode_List.SourceCode:
/**
 * Write a description of class test here.
 *
 * @author (your name)
 * @version (a version number or a date)
 */
public class KKBOx
{
    static double l;
    static double w;
    static double h;


static double volume(double l, double w, double h)
{
    double ans=l*w*h;
    return ans;
}  

public static void main(Double[] n)
{
   l=2;
   w=3;
   h=4;
   System.out.println(ans);
}
}

Error.Message:
新增物件動作
KKBOx b = new KKBOx(l,w,h);
呼叫時用b.volume();

因為建構子有參數，所以呼叫建構子也需要給參數
若要將參數識別字當成屬性，要用this存取屬性
KKbox(double length,double width,double height)
{
	this.l=l;
    	this.w=w;
    	this.h=h;
}

產生物件括號裡不用加上參數，且要回傳一個值
double volume()
{
	double ans=l*w*h;
	return ans;
}
